# Engine layer

## Core classes (`engine/main/`)

| Class | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `Registry` | Service container (`$registry->db`, `$registry->user`) |
| `Load` | Load views, models, libraries |
| `Action` | Parse URI, dispatch controller |
| `DB` | Database abstraction |
| `Config` | Loads `application/config.php` |

## Libraries (`engine/libs/`)

- `ssh2.php`, `sftp.php` — remote location communication
- `query.php` + drivers — game server query (SAMP, MTA, Valve, RAGE:MP, Minecraft)
- `mail.php`, `pagination.php`, `validate.php`

## Games (`engine/games/game_settings.php`)

Defines MCPE cores, RAGE:MP node module URLs, binary paths. Large static array.

## FTP (`engine/engine_ftp/`)

elFinder-based file manager for server FTP access. Do not refactor lightly.
